The paper discusses a new approach to searching for nonlinear combinations of attributes in various data analytic communities, such as regression, decision list, and association rule hunting. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), data mining (cs.DM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), statistics (cs.ST), and information theory (cs.IT). Among these, cs.LG and cs.DM are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the paper's focus on searching for nonlinear combinations of attributes.
